{
  "stem": "22803.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And opposite to what they do in America, the little ones were in the back instead of in the front, so I was always in the back.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wasn't very sporty, so all these things didn't make school that terribly happy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Later on in high school, I-- I was good, I guess, in math and physics.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I-- some teachers were already-- first of all, I was very fidgety child and I would always talk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And also, some of the teachers were already-- you know, there were some anti-Semitic teachers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember-- I mean, I wasn't brought up in a way that you come home and there you have a bad mark, because-- I mean, that wasn't done, absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- but I remember in the last year of high school, we had cooking lessons, because at that time it was-- yeah, we had cooking as a related subject.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we cooked a meal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we had to learn to serve and do all this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at the end, a dispute broke out about who had to do the cleaning up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it became-- I was the only Jewish child, and it became a confrontation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I felt I was in the right and I spoke up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the teacher disappeared into another room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She didn't want to get involved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You see, they were afraid already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And one or two others of my co-students backed me, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But the teacher, it was definitely by that time, them and us thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And as I said, I was the only Jewish child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I-- I spoke up, but the teacher did not defend me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- I had a couple-- I spoke up and I was sort of cornered.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
